default£500,000
defaultNetwork Rail Infrastructure Limited
defaultNetwork Rail’s failure to act on substantial evidence that pedestrians using the crossing had insufficient sight of approaching trains. Pedestrians were therefore exposed to an increased safety risk when using the crossing. This resulted in the death at the footpath.
